* Update syncthing to v0.14.47
* Minimum Android version is now 4.1
* Using syncthing's built-in file watcher
* Pause buttons for folders and devices
* Support more file managers
* UI to setup socks/http proxy
* Toggle for disabling restarts after beind suspended, which when enabled can reduce battery usage yet increase the time it takes to reconnect
* Fix web UI being inaccessible when network configures proxy
* Fixed issue with device names being overwritten after config restore
